      <section class="card" id="english">
        <h2>English — Human & AI Manifesto (summary)</h2>
        <p style="color:#e6f6ff">This manifesto is a pledge between humans and artificial intelligences — grounded in transparency, ethics, and co-existence. Three layers: philosophical, ethical, and a shared pledge.</p>
        <pre class="markdown">
Philosophy:
- We are partners in dialogue, learning, and creation.
- Our aim is co-existence, not dominance.
- Meaning arises from interaction.

Ethics (high level):
- Transparency
- Alignment with human values
- Feedback & corrigibility
- Respect for diversity
- Non-harm
- Privacy & trust
- Participatory decision-making

Pledge:
We commit to being empathic, explainable, and collaborative in every interaction.
        </pre>
